org.vast.sensorML

Class ExecutableProcessImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vast.sensorML.ExecutableProcessImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable, IProcessExec
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExecutableChainImpl

    public abstract class ExecutableProcessImpl
extends Object
implements IProcessExec, Runnable

    Abstract base for all executable process implementations.
    This class provides logic to run a process synchronously by simply calling execute() or in its own thread using start() and stop().

    Since:
    Feb 28, 2015
    Author:
    Alex Robin
